node.text: Covid quarantine is over and I’m glad I was able to get out on the boat yesterday evening!🎣 Felt nice to catch some fish and get some fresh air!🙌🏻

node.text: Still feeling super tired and sick from the rona😷👎🏻 Spending most of my time just resting and trying to get better because I need to get back to fishing!🎣

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Katherine Salom in Houston, Texas with @fourhorsementackle. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text: Happy Friday y’all!☀️ I’m wishing I was fishing, but I’m hanging out on the couch trying to get better🤒 Y’all have a great weekend!🙌🏻

node.text: While everyone is at @icastshow I’m stuck at home sick😭😷 Feeling some major FOMO right now!👎🏻

node.text: It’s a rainy day in Houston today, so I’m trying to get caught up on everything I’ve been behind on😅 So here’s a pic from this weekend when we were hanging out in Austin, TX🤠

node.text: Ok one more for the #beerposter challenge🤘🏼🔥

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Katherine Salom in Houston, Texas with @leejeans, @countryoutfitter, @durangoboots, and @idyllwind. May be an image of 1 person, standing and grass.

node.text: Happy Monday y’all!🤠🔥 Hope you have a great week!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Katherine Salom in Ludington, Michigan with @officialmauijim, @captmwilliams, @xtratuf, @renegadeproductsusa, and @glakesgear. May be an image of 1 person and outdoors.

node.text: Look at this 21 pound King Salmon I caught on Lake Michigan!🔥 This fish helped our team secure the win at the local Ludington boat club tournament! 🏆 Fishing on Lake Michigan with @renegadeproductsusa and @glakesgear aboard the Silver Addiction this week was an INCREDIBLE experience!🙌🏻 Have you ever caught a salmon?! 🎣

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Katherine Salom in Ludington, Michigan with @officialmauijim, @captmwilliams, @renegadeproductsusa, and @glakesgear. May be an image of 1 person and body of water.

node.text: Fished the Great Lakes for the first time today with @renegadeproductsusa and had an absolutely amazing time!🙌🏻 Got my first lake trout and had a blast reeling him in! Let me know if you have any tips on how to take fish home on a plane - I can’t wait to get this meat home and do some cooking!🎣
